'''VDPAU''' ('''Video Decode and Presentation API for Unix''')是一个最初由[[NVIDIA|NVIDIA]]开发的针对其GeForce 8系列以及更高系列的[[GPU|GPU]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lists.freedesktop.org/archives/xorg-announce/2009-September/001036.html |title=Announcing libvdpau 0.2 |access-date=2011-01-19 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224023726/https://lists.freedesktop.org/archives/xorg-announce/2009-September/001036.html }}</ref><ref name="phoronix.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=NzU0MA |title=NVIDIA Releases Standalone VDPAU Library |access-date=2011-01-19 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308122840/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=NzU0MA }}</ref>
，在[[UNIX|UNIX]]和[[类UNIX|类UNIX]]系统（包括 [[Linux|Linux]]、[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]和[[Solaris|Solaris]]）下基于[[X_Window系统|X Window系统]]下的开源库(libvdpau)和[[API|API]]。 VDPAU的API可以让[[视频播放器|视频播放器]]把一部分的视频解码和视频图像补偿交给[[GPU|GPU]]<ref name ='vdpau_dxva'>{{cite web
 |url          = http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=article&item=nvidia_180_vdpau&num=1
 |title        = NVIDIA Driver Brings PureVideo Features To Linux
 |accessdate   = 2009-03-13
 |author       = [[Michael_Larabel|Michael Larabel]]
 |date         = 2008-11-14
